title: [Teras Isle, Moor]
description: Sky, sea, and soil blend together in a monotonous haze of darkness.  The only breaks in the dreary sameness are the occasional sulfurous mist that drifts down the volcanic slopes to the north and the jagged black line to the east that marks the cliffs known as the Dark Palisade.

Sky, sea, and soil blend together in a monotonous haze of grey.  The only breaks in the dreary sameness are the occasional sulfurous mist that drifts down the volcanic slopes to the north and the jagged black line to the east that marks the cliffs known as the Dark Palisade.
